{
  "products": {
    "accounting": {
      "enabled": false,
      "client_id": "",
      "oauth": {
        "authorize_url": "https://api.biz.moneyforward.com/authorize",
        "token_url": "https://api.biz.moneyforward.com/token",
        "redirect_uri": "http://localhost:8765/callback",
        "client_auth": "client_secret_basic",
        "scopes": [
          "mfc/admin/tenant.read",
          "mfc/accounting/offices.read",
          "mfc/accounting/accounts.read",
          "mfc/accounting/taxes.read",
          "mfc/accounting/trade_partners.read",
          "mfc/accounting/journal.read",
          "mfc/accounting/journal.write"
        ]
      },
      "api": {
        "base": "",
        "offices_url": "https://api.biz.moneyforward.com/v2/tenant"
      }
    },
    "expense": {
      "enabled": false,
      "client_id": "",
      "oauth": {
        "authorize_url": "https://expense.moneyforward.com/oauth/authorize",
        "token_url": "https://expense.moneyforward.com/oauth/token",
        "redirect_uri": "https://expense.moneyforward.com/api/oauth2-redirect.html",
        "scopes": []
      },
      "api": { "base": "https://expense.moneyforward.com/api" }
    }
  },
  "_notes": [
    "会計(accounting)と経費(expense)は別の OAuth サーバ・別の client_id/secret(片方の資格情報は他方で使えない)。",
    "非秘密(URL/scopes/client_id)はここ、秘密(client_secret)はルート共有 .env の",
    "  MONEYFORWARD_ACCOUNTING_CLIENT_SECRET / MONEYFORWARD_EXPENSE_CLIENT_SECRET に置く。",
    "各フィールドの解決順: MONEYFORWARD_<PRODUCT>_<FIELD>(env) → この products.<product> の値。",
    "authorize_url/token_url は公式の既定値を記入済み。scopes は使う API のリファレンス/Swagger で確認して追記。",
    "会計の api.offices_url = 認可サーバ v2 の /v2/tenant(疎通確認の呼び先。2026-06-14 実機検証済)。",
    "  /v2/tenant は scope mfc/admin/tenant.read が必須・応答は {tenant_code, tenant_name} の単一オブジェクト。",
    "手順: docs/setup/moneyforward-api-setup.md"
  ]
}
